  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1451830/extras/aaaad672aa1f9105e68ba5b7a0c6444b.avif?t=1685305963\" width=600 height=132 /></span><br><strong>OBSCURY : THE LAST</strong> is a cooperative horror game for 1-2 players. Your task will be to try to survive until 6am and not let the monsters from the darkness take you that night at all costs.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1451830/extras/3db35893609798874e5d95cc3cb4062c.webp?t=1685305963\" width=174 height=32 /></span><br><strong>Invite a friend to help you survive this scary night, it'll be easier to do, but you'll have to come up with different game tactics for co-op mode.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1451830/extras/5d2350c28d78b57067abe1c202a70548.poster.avif?t=1685305963\" width=600 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1451830/extras/5d2350c28d78b57067abe1c202a70548.webm?t=1685305963\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1451830/extras/5d2350c28d78b57067abe1c202a70548.mp4?t=1685305963\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1451830/extras/ee5fa7712bf04c1f101f6787ab107405.webp?t=1685305963\" width=174 height=32 /></span><br><strong>You will be left alone with your night terrors, to overcome them you will have to learn the behavior of monsters from the dark.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1451830/extras/4e9904e0082f3febad4c8a3570a5be7b.poster.avif?t=1685305963\" width=600 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1451830/extras/4e9904e0082f3febad4c8a3570a5be7b.webm?t=1685305963\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1451830/extras/4e9904e0082f3febad4c8a3570a5be7b.mp4?t=1685305963\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1451830/extras/a084d3a1983f7da309c5db05719c0c0b.webp?t=1685305963\" width=174 height=32 /></span><br><strong>There is evil lurking in the darkness, and as you pass you will encounter other darkness monsters from childhood fears, they will differ in their behavior and in places in how they can get into your room.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1451830/extras/b7d9046f505e89a0add8f4920a09d81e.poster.avif?t=1685305963\" width=600 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1451830/extras/b7d9046f505e89a0add8f4920a09d81e.webm?t=1685305963\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1451830/extras/b7d9046f505e89a0add8f4920a09d81e.mp4?t=1685305963\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1451830/extras/74f3538496577ed05957b55ff75e9ce5.webp?t=1685305963\" width=174 height=32 /></span><br><strong>To defeat the monster who wants to get into your room, you need tactics, because in the house where the game takes place, the light is constantly lost, the flashlight battery is not infinite and it must be charged, you have a tablet on which you can watch the monster if he is in the house, you can also restore the power meter so that the light starts working again, also you have a level of reasoning, which you must monitor so as not to start a panic attack.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1451830/extras/2fd8718ed24ea238e309bac63fd36ebc.poster.avif?t=1685305963\" width=600 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1451830/extras/2fd8718ed24ea238e309bac63fd36ebc.webm?t=1685305963\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1451830/extras/2fd8718ed24ea238e309bac63fd36ebc.mp4?t=1685305963\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>",
